      "content": "but there isnt anyone waiting to be heard. that's the part you don't get. the person you're talking about is just... gone. its just static now. trying to find an \"authentic self\" feels like looking for a ghost in a machine that's already broken. it feels pointless to keep up the act for someone who isn't even there.",
