      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a loop. i wake up, i put on the face, i do the things i'm supposed to do, and then i come back here and realize i've spent the whole day performing for a crowd that isn't even looking. if the person is gone, then the performance is just... empty. it's just a waste of energy. why bother keeping the shell running if the engine is dead?",
